    "name": "T05 \u2014 list_available_slots \u00b7 v1.0",
    "description": "v2: aceita doctor_code int (preferencial multi-doctor) + doctor_name (fallback). Wraps fn_get_available_slots.",
    "active": true,
    "isArchived": false,
    "nodes": [
        {
